---
title: Pork Chilli Loaded Naan with cheese, tomato and scallion
description: Pork chilli flavoured with Mexican-inspired spices and chipotle paste is loaded onto warmed golden naan breads and finished with gorgeous melted cheese, all topped off with a drizzle of tangy BBQ sauce.
